parameters.name: DiagType
parameters.description: Type of diagnosis, indicating which diagnostic rules are hit.

parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description:
Number of items per page in a paginated query. The maximum value is 100.

Default value:

- If no value is set or the set value is less than 20, the default value is 20.
- If the set value is greater than 100, the default value is 100.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: NextToken for the next page. Include this value when requesting the next page.
